title: Shu Caverns Of The Nightjars-HI2U
description:
Shu: Caverns Of The Nightjars (c) Coatsink

Release 05/28/2017

Protection: Steam
Game Size: 1 DISC
Game Type: Action, Adventure, Indie [RELEASE NOTES]
Shu is a stylish 2.5D platformer set in a beautiful and
engrossing world. Guide Shu and a cast of beautifully hand-drawn
characters as they run, jump and glide their way across exotic
lands, forever pursued by the monstrous and unrelenting Storm
Can you outrun the end of the world?

Caverns Of The Nightjars includes:
* 6 new levels
* New character combinations
* More Collectables
* New Achievements
* New Time Trial records to beat

This release contains all previous updates and dlc's! 

[INSTALL NOTES] 

1. Mount / burn image 
2. Install 
3. Copy content from 'Crack' folder and replace game dir files 
4. Play game 
5. If U like it, buy it!
